     et al.  “Serious adverse events” faced by clinical trials. ﻿ <i xmlns:helper="urn:XsltStringHelper"> Indian J Med Paediatr Oncol</i>. 2020;41(2):127. doi:<a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.4103/ijmpo.ijmpo_114_20">10.4103/ijmpo.ijmpo_114_20</a><a class="google-scholar-ref-link" href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=%E2%80%9CSerious%20adverse%20events%E2%80%9D%20faced%20by%20clinical%20trials.&amp;author=PM%20Parikh&amp;author=P%20Mehta&amp;author=KM%20Mvt&amp;publication_year=2020&amp;journal=Indian%20J%20Med%20Paediatr%20Oncol&amp;volume=41&amp;pages=127" target="_blank" xmlns:helper="urn:XsltStringHelper">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div> 
    </div>

