         GD﻿, 
     et al.  Reporting clinical studies affected by the COVID-19 pandemic. ﻿ <i xmlns:helper="urn:XsltStringHelper"> JAMA Netw Open</i>. 2021;4(1):e2036155. doi:<a href="http://jamanetwork.com/article.aspx?doi=10.1001/jamanetworkopen.2020.36155">10.1001/jamanetworkopen.2020.36155</a><a class="pubmed-link" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33443576" target="_blank" xmlns:helper="urn:XsltStringHelper">PubMed</a><a class="google-scholar-ref-link" href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Reporting%20clinical%20studies%20affected%20by%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.&amp;author=RH%20Perlis&amp;author=SJPA%20Haneuse&amp;author=GD%20Rubenfeld&amp;publication_year=2021&amp;journal=JAMA%20Netw%20Open&amp;volume=4&amp;pages=" target="_blank" xmlns:helper="urn:XsltStringHelper">Google Scholar</a></div></div><div class="reference"><a class="reference-number" id="jsc210001r52">52.</a><div class="reference-content">McDermott
